OL,4,Ccriminal offence'
OL,6,FLabour pledged in its manifesto to
OL,7,Fintroduce a new offence for spiking,
OL,8,Fbut it is unclear when the legislation
OL,9,Fwill be brought in, as ITV News'
OL,10,FStacey Foster reports
OL,12,FSir Keir Starmer has reiterated plans
OL,13,Fto make spiking a 'criminal offence'
OL,14,Fas he lays out plans for venue staff
OL,15,Fto be trained in how to deal with
OL,16,Fthese incidents to tackle violence
OL,17,Fagainst women and girls.
OL,19,FIn a post on X, the prime minister
OL,20,Fsaid: "Spiking will be made a criminal
OL,21,Foffence.
