OL,6,F"My government was elected to take
OL,7,Fback our streets, central to this
OL,8,Fmission is making sure women and girls
OL,9,Fcan feel safe at night.
OL,11,F"Perpetrators of spiking will feel the
OL,12,Ffull force of the law."
OL,14,FThe government says the pledge is part
OL,15,Fof its promise to halve violence
OL,16,Fagainst women and girls in the next
OL,17,Fdecade as Starmer said he hopes the
OL,18,Fchange will give people "the
OL,19,Fconfidence to come forward".
