OL,3,CKeir Starmer: 'Spiking will be made a
OL,4,Ccriminal offence'
OL,6,FSpiking is already illegal, but the
OL,7,Fcommitment is to making it a specific
OL,8,Foffence. According to information
OL,9,Fpublished by the Metropolitan Police,
OL,10,Fspiking offences are covered by more
OL,11,Fthan one law, but most come under the
OL,12,FOffences Against the Person Act 1861.
OL,14,FIt is unclear when the new legislation
OL,15,Fwill be introduced, but ministers and
OL,16,Fofficials are understood to be working
OL,17,Fto bring it forward as soon as
OL,18,Fpossible.
