OL,6,FSaraya Haddad had her drink spiked
OL,7,Ffive years ago while on a night out at
OL,8,Funiversity.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV News, she said: "The
OL,11,Flast thing I remember is being
OL,12,Fslightly tipsey, but nothing more than
OL,13,Fthat - and then black out. I woke up
OL,14,Fin my bed 13 hours later the next
OL,15,Fmorning."
