OL,6,FOn Monday, the government announced
OL,7,Fplans for 10,000 workers in the
OL,8,Fhospitality industry to be trained to
OL,9,Fdeal with incidents by next spring as
OL,10,Fpart of an expansion of a scheme
OL,11,Fpiloted from December.
OL,13,FWorkers in the night-time economy will
OL,14,Fbe instructed on how to prevent cases,
OL,15,Fsupport victims and help "collect
OL,16,Fevidence" by spring next year, Number
OL,17,F10 said.
