OL,6,FLabour pledged in its manifesto to
OL,7,Fintroduce a new offence for spiking,
OL,8,Fbut there was no detail in the King's
OL,9,FSpeech this year about a specific
OL,10,Fcrime, though it promised to ensure an
OL,11,Fimproved police response to cases.
OL,13,FPlain clothes officers are being
OL,14,Fdeployed in areas around bars and
OL,15,Fclubs to spot predatory behaviour,
OL,16,Fwith Chief Constable Jason Hogg of
OL,17,FThames Valley Police due to set out
OL,18,Fhow his force is implementing such
OL,19,Fmeasures.
