OL,6,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper said:
OL,7,F"Spiking is a disturbing and serious
OL,8,Fcrime which can have a damaging and
OL,9,Flong-lasting impact on victims.
OL,11,F"That's why today we are taking
OL,12,Fdecisive action to prevent this
OL,13,Fdevastating crime and to crack down on
OL,14,Fperpetrators, by introducing a new
OL,15,Fcriminal offence for spiking and
OL,16,Flaunching specialist training for
OL,17,Fthousands of bar staff nationwide.
